        <p>Mr. Jaydeep Kotadiya, an accomplished Ceramic Art teacher, currently holds a position in the sculpture department at Surat College of Fine Art, VNSGU. He earned his bachelor's degree in sculpture and completed his master's in Ceramic from Santiniketan, West Bengal, in 2018. Since then, he has showcased his expertise through various art exhibitions and actively participated in workshops.</p>
