                    Established in November 2015, Mudberry Studio has become a hub for pottery enthusiasts in Surat, Gujarat. Founded by passionate ceramic artists, the studio started with a modest setup and has since evolved into a fully-equipped space, fostering creativity and skill development. Inspired by Gujarat's cultural heritage, Mudberry Studio is committed to reviving traditional craftsmanship while embracing contemporary artistic trends.
